text: While highlighting growing bilateral trade & financial linkages between our two friendly countries, I underscored the immense importance Pakistan attaches to strategic ML-1 railway, Babusar Tunnel, Karachi Circular Railway & desalination plant in Karachi.
translated_text: While highlighting growing bilateral trade & financial linkages between our two friendly countries, I underlined the immense importance Pakistan attaches to strategic ML-1 railway, Babusar Tunnel, Karachi Circular Railway & Desalination plant in Karachi.

text: We have allocated billions of rupees for targeted subsidies. This amount is in addition to Rs. 344 billion allocated for BISP. Only deserving people to get the subsidy.
translated_text: We have allocated billions of rupees for targeted subsidies. This amount is in addition to Rs. 344 billion allocated for BISP. Only deserving people to get the subsidy.

text: Government has taken this decision for the purpose of poverty alleviation. We have asked our affluent segment of society to fulfil the national duty by sharing the burden, for it is the poor who have always borne the brunt & rendered sacrifices for the country.
translated_text: Government has taken this decision for the purpose of poverty alleviation. We have asked our affluent segment of society to fulfill the national duty by sharing the burden, for it is the poor who have always borne the brunt & rendered sacrifices for the country.

text: Mindful of the financial difficulties of the employees in public sector, the government has given a raise of 15% & merger of ad hoc allowance in their basic pay.
translated_text: Mindful of the financial difficulties of the employees in the public sector, the government has given a raise of 15% & merger of ad hoc allowance in their basic pay.

text: While we have had excellent human resource, fertile lands & plans, what we have lacked all along is the will to turn strategies into concrete actions. We have faltered on executing the projects leading to cost & time overruns. We need to break this logjam that has held us back.
translated_text: While we have had excellent human resource, fertile lands & plans, what we have lacked all along is the will to turn strategies into concrete actions. We have faltered on executing the projects leading to cost & time overruns. We need to break this logjam that has held us back.

text: This is the first budget that contains the plan for revival of the economy. The hard decisions we have taken will enable the country to overcome the economic crisis. The government has tried its best to place minimum burden on lower income & salaried class.
translated_text: This is the first budget that contains the plan for revival of the economy. The hard decisions we have taken will enable the country to overcome the economic crisis. The government has tried its best to place minimum burden on lower income & salaried class.

text: The tax slabs have been revised. Those earning up to Rs. 1.2 million (12 lakh rupay) annually have been exempted from taxes.
translated_text: The tax slabs have been revised. Those earning up to Rs. 1.2 million (12 lakh rupees) annually have been exempted from taxes.

text: Our citizens will be able to notarize their important legal documents such as marriage certificate, degrees and more via MOFA designated officials in Pakistan which will be internationally accepted without the need for any further verification. https://t.co/dSjtOZZyZr
translated_text: Our citizens will be able to notarize their important legal documents such as marriage certificate, degrees and more via MOFA designated officials in Pakistan which will be internationally accepted without the need for any further verification. https://t.co/dSjtOZZyZr

text: Macroeconomic stability is the first step. What the coalition government is aiming to achieve is economic self-sufficiency. This precisely is the spirit of the budget. Our national security is very closely tied to economic reliance.
translated_text: Macroeconomic stability is the first step. What the coalition government is aiming to achieve is economic self-sufficiency. This precisely is the spirit of the budget. Our national security is very closely tied to economic reliance.

text: Punjab has seen the worst-ever misgovernance. Citizens were deprived of free medicines & scholarships. Civil & police transfers/postings were on sale. Quality of municipal services plummeted & lawlessness became rampant. Manner in which Punjab was treated was an insult to people.
translated_text: Punjab has seen the worst-ever misgovernance. Citizens were deprived of free medicines & scholarships. Civil & Police transfers/postings were on sale. Quality of municipal services plummeted & lawlessness became rampant. Manner in which Punjab was treated was an insult to people.

text: When the coalition government got into power, it had 2 paths open to it; whether to go for elections & leave the economy broken or address the economic challenges first. We opted to save Pakistan from economic quagmire even if it involved political risks. We put Pakistan first.
translated_text: When the coalition government got into power, it had 2 paths open to it; whether to go for elections & leave the economy broken or address the economic challenges first. We opted to save Pakistan from economic quagmire even if it involved political risks. We put Pakistan first.

text: Zero tax has been announced for import of agricultural machinery and implants. This major step will enable our farmers & agriculture to progress.
translated_text: Zero tax has been announced for import of agricultural machinery and implants. This major step will enable our farmers & agriculture to progress.

text: This facilitation in the visa regime is aimed at bringing both countries closer, helping Afghan people & attracting business and investment from wider Central Asian region. I have directed Interior Ministry to work on a more liberal visa policy. https://t.co/53gloeyBPC
translated_text: This facilitation in the visa regime is aimed at bringing both countries closer, helping Afghan people & Attracting business and investment from wider Central Asian region. I have directed the Interior Ministry to work on a more liberal visa policy. https://t.co/53gloeyBPC

text: Let me make two things absolutely clear here. First, it is a direct tax on the income of people & industries falling in certain categories of income. Secondly, the proceeds from this measure will be spent in the most productive of ways for people facing financial constraints.
translated_text: Let me make two things absolutely clear here. First, it is a direct tax on the income of people & industries falling in certain categories of income. Secondly, the proceeds from this measure will be spent in the most productive ways for people facing financial constraints.

text: Government has decided to tax non-productive assets of the rich including 5% tax on purchase of second property & increase in tax on luxury cars.
translated_text: Government has decided to tax non-productive assets of the rich including 5% tax on purchase of second property & increase in tax on luxury cars.

text: Your vote is power. Use this power to reject the politics of anarchy, division & hate. Our beautiful country is much more than what this man has reduced it to. Cast your vote for national development & bright future of your children. I have my faith in your power to choose.
